occurred at the level of single

00:43:47.000 --> 00:43:51.000
cells, and that all this amazing
diversity we see around us was very

00:43:51.000 --> 00:43:56.000
recent embellishments in evolution.
So that means when you study

00:43:56.000 --> 00:44:00.000
