00:44:08.000 --> 00:44:12.000
coli, if you look inside a yeast and
you look inside one of our cells you

00:44:12.000 --> 00:44:16.000
find that, to a huge extent,
many, many of the cellular

00:44:16.000 --> 00:44:20.000
components are common.
They arose similarly in evolution

00:44:20.000 --> 00:44:24.000
